    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant stop thinking about how none of this actually matters. like, even if i do everything \"right\" or try to be a good person, the universe is just gonna end in heat death anyway. every single thing we do, every feeling, every struggle... it's just static. it feels so heavy knowing that there's literally no point to any of it.",
